[SN]TITLE[SN]
Gang shoot man in legs in Meadowbrook in Craigavon

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
A man has been shot in the legs in Craigavon, County Armagh.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
A number of men forced their way into a house in Meadowbrook shortly after 23:00 GMT on Wednesday.
A 26-year-old man who was in the house was taken outside by the gang and shot.
He was taken to hospital and is described as being in a stable condition. Police have appealed for anyone with information to contact them.
